social_posts.post_text: Merry Christmas! 🎁🎄❤️🤪

I’ll stop posting Flapper shit when it’s 2030 😇
Big thankies to @hurricane_butterfly for letting me borrow this beauty- it’s an authentic Thompson full auto machine gun that I just HAD to model! 🔥😍
And I’ll stop posting Babydoll… never💀
Back on my nursing school grind 👩🏼‍⚕️🦠🩺

I made this video way too long and I’m still learning how to not be AWKWARD on video! Forgive me. Let’s break down the mystery of how or why my photo appeared in a Chinese/Hong Kong video game… #Storytime #StolenArt #KnivesOut #Whytho 🤔🔪
(2016) Worth a re-share! ⚓️
How it started vs. how it’s going 💀

1. Raiding @hurricane_butterfly’s collection is my favorite
2. YES THESE ARE OLD PHOTOS AND IDC because nursing school has been kicking my bootay, okay? In the words of my dad, “If it was easy, everyone would do it.” 🙃
3. The dirndl WILL returndl

Last weekend was my 30th birthday celebration… so of course I bought a ridiculous dress and THEN realized that there’s absolutely nowhere in Lancaster, Pennsylvania I could wear this. My BF said, “Maybe the strip club?” 🤣💀 This reel is made of live photos- might try more of this kind of content style in the future because it’s pretty easy to do! 💋 #Glamour #Snubby #Louboutins
Just more pix of me from my birthday weekend (it was April 20th)! The vintage nurse drawing of me is by @alphalimaechoxrayw 👩🏼‍⚕️💕 #StudentNurse #LancasterPA #intothepinkreef

You can make fun of me all you want, but I’ve been a Taylor Swift fan since the beginning! 🤠✨ She put on an absolutely beautiful and flawless performance! After everything I went through to PULL STRAIGHT As in nursing school this semester, this experience truly felt like such a reward. ❤️ For #ErasTourPhilly, I copied one of her recent outfits… so maybe my #ErasTourOutfit is a #TaylorSwiftCosplay!? 😜

Happy Independence Day! 🇺🇸✨ 
My gorgeous new silver/blue rifle was custom built for me by my friends at @axismfg in Spokane, WA. Today seems like the perfect day to show it off! I’m looking ok these days, too. 😜 #IndependenceDay #AmericanGirl
I’m f*cking crazy, but I’m FREE! 🦅🤠🇺🇸
THIS BARBIE has been working hard on the cardiac unit all summer! 👩🏼‍⚕️🫀

Happy to announce that Nate and I are engaged! 💍❤️ Thank you to my sister @tyedyechey for capturing Nate’s proposal- I was truly surprised and started crying. We’re so happy. #Proposal #Engagement #IsaidYes #LongwoodGardens

Was able to sneak in a photo shoot with photographer @camilo.e.morales right before my last grueling semester of nursing school started up! Love how these elegant film portraits turned out. Also my first shoot ever wearing my engagement ring! 📸💍✨☺️ #Portrait #FilmPhotography #VintageDress

Picking out my favorite shots in between studying for my abdominal trauma/hepatic failure test 🤓📚 
📸: @camilo.e.morales in Frederick, Maryland
#Boudoir #Portrait #FrederickMD
Oktoberfest is the OktoberBEST 🍺🤪

Christmas is coming in hot!!!!
